headline.print_headline: United Flight Makes Emergency Landing in Canada
headline.main: United Flight Makes Emergency Landing in Canada

lead_paragraph: A spokesman for the airport in Halifax, Nova Scotia, says a United Airlines Boeing 777 airliner on its way to Brussels from the U.S. has made an emergency landing after a fire on the aircraft.
